Interface JaxbContextBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JaxbContextBuilder.Builder

    public interface JaxbContextBuilder
    The jaxb context builder creates a JAXBContext from the provided meta data JaxbContextData.
    Author:
    Christian Bremer
